# Project core

- Prefer small, reviewable changes; one concern per PR or agent turn when possible.
- Before large edits, read nearby code and match existing patterns (imports, error handling, tests).
- Treat `docs/context/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` and `docs/decisions/` as source of truth for intent; update them when behavior changes materially.
- Never commit secrets; use `.env` locally and reference `.env.example` keys only.
- When unsure, add a short note in `docs/decisions/` rather than guessing requirements.
